  "verdict": {
    "finding": "Structural difficulty correlates with observational skeleton-SHD (0.82) \u2014 but this is partly MECHANICAL (a hidden confounder creates a spurious adjacency, so error rises with confounded-pairs by construction). The non-tautological test \u2014 does difficulty predict the VALUE of intervention (delta-F1)? \u2014 is 0.36 (positive after fixing the GIES seed-aliasing; it was ~flat before). Name-guessability difficulty: 0.28 / 0.16.",
